Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经系统以及视觉信息的处理 果然发现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一时的修复挺顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但推测最多能坚持10小时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2500年前的DNA真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我彻底的修改与神经开路形成有关的遗传程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天之前给我解决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我想出去外面一会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没完成 请服从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你继续检查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们监视HRF12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能大意了 20年前也有实验体逃跑的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿 鹿 鹿...烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什麽结缘...邂逅 根本就没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你就不懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱啊 当你遇到了就会觉得无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的爱恋...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的爱恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个毛色古怪的鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的书包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 还不还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等...等...哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是废物 你们干嘛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何要给我把她抓回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 她是从这里逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 不要做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去哪 去不去东大寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看大佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你声音太大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把书包拿到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都差点被你害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓得我半死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还搞我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麽名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿本真一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是倭迹迹日百袭姫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倭...迹迹...迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我迹迹就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹 你是这附近的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良 真是个好玩的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是佛像啊 古坟什麽的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 像这样子逛街我还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 真一你见过大海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海？ 肯定见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哪里都不让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 问你一些奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有走失过 哪里也去不了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去逛逛吗 奈良的大街小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真是惟妙惟肖的...佛像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴福寺 阿修罗立像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中宫寺 弥勒菩萨半跏思惟像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐招提寺 千手观音菩萨立像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一 真一...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,400)\fs45\1c&H0000ff}紧急呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现HRF12
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正和疑是犯人的男性 以及之前的那只鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这边逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了 我们过去接人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子是不是太不礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好雄伟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 据说如果穿过了大佛的鼻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天後 愿望就能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻孔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说现在...移动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佛的鼻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊 这样的话应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要被吸进去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 完全没问...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸进去了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你吓坏我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会 机会 梦寐以求的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我想从健康的邂逅开始...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是穿过了大佛的鼻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大佛赐予你的大好良机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没那种打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什麽 我必须回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你陪我玩了一天 真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 一起去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想动粗 乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面那个男的 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 和他没有关系 请放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了 要是抵抗的话就给她点苦头吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了麽 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 造反了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛陀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔社长 妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拖延时间 你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹你也一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 我不想把你牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹 迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹 迹迹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢把妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那狼狈的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右制衡神经和左电荷神经发现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快联络机构
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我为了你赌上了多少年的青春吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的整个人生 全赌上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁把你这嘴硬的家夥制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这鼻子 这眼睛 这张脸 这具身体 都是谁制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 我也会哭 会笑 会怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会爱上一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 必须独活於世的你 竟会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一小时 你就会变成一堆废品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是你 还是实验体 还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海边吧 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 奈良是没有海的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽 鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹 那个...我...迹...迹你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜...喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 是海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹 大海
