Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:20:01.85,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉坂 吾见人 何有 依以 亦一目见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪里去了 担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是和女的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:28.38,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萍水相逢情根种 何以共君再聚首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:28.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉坂 吾见人 何有 依以 亦一目见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什麽 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迹迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
